      "seed": 689934,
      "text": "🕵️  Like a QA engineer reviewing a bug report:\n   1) Figure out which screen type it is\n   2) Read all the data fields off the screenshot\n   3) Check every field against the schema\n   4) If errors: fix the prompt and retry (max 2×)\n   5) Check game-logic rules (HP ≤ max, pity ≥ 0)\n   6) File a structured report with all findings",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🕵️  Like a QA engineer reviewing a bug report:\n   1) Figure out which screen type it is\n   2) Read all the data fields off the screenshot\n   3) Check every field against the schema\n   4) If errors: fix the prompt and retry (max 2×)\n   5) Check game-logic rules (HP ≤ max, pity ≥ 0)\n   6) File a structured report with all findings",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.5
    },
