      "seed": 9747,
      "text": "📡  agents/observability.py  —  TraceLog\n   Like a GPS flight recorder for the pipeline:\n   every node entry/exit, token count ($$$), and retry\n   event is timestamped and stored in TraceLog.\n   Exports JSON for post-hoc debugging & cost accounting.\n   summary() → {total_cost_usd, vlm_calls, retries, errors}",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "📡  agents/observability.py  —  TraceLog\n   Like a GPS flight recorder for the pipeline:\n   every node entry/exit, token count ($$$), and retry\n   event is timestamped and stored in TraceLog.\n   Exports JSON for post-hoc debugging & cost accounting.\n   summary() → {total_cost_usd, vlm_calls, retries, errors}",
